commit.message:
(movsf+1,2,movdf+1,2): Make 'f' preferred register class.

From-SVN: r6115

@@ -148,8 +148,8 @@
 ;; to recombine a mem -> mem move
 ;; 
 (define_insn ""
-  [(set (match_operand:DF 0 "register_operand" "=rf")
